{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ad Memoriam is an in-development mystery game about a band with a curse: at every single one of their concerts, someone dies in an accident. When Erica - Ad Memoriam superfan, amateur detective, and Alicia\u2019s best friend - becomes the next victim, Alicia realizes that the deaths may not be as accidental as they seem. Play as Alicia while she follows the band and the trail of bodies that they leave behind, and discover the truth in Ad Memoriam's history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EXPLORE THE SCENE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891230/extras/20241014170722_1.jpg?t=1739181728\" />Walk through each concert venue and get a lay of the land before and after a victim dies. Search for clues, spot any inconsistencies, and find evidence to back up your theories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>NOBODY KNOWS THE TRUTH</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891230/extras/20241014202359_1.jpg?t=1739181728\" />Interview other concertgoers and venue staff about what they've seen. In a setting as hectic and crowded as a concert, there's bound to be lots of witnesses - but can any of them be trusted to give an accurate testimony?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>RECONSTRUCT THE INCIDENT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2891230/extras/20241014200826_1.jpg?t=1739181728\" />Use witness accounts to identify the sequence of events that lead up to each accident. Piece together the truth from half-remembered details, conflicting testimonies, and lies. Put the chaos of the incident in order, and discover the truth behind each death.</p><p clas